snippet.title: 2021 Anime Year in Review (Part 1)
snippet.description:
Here is my review of year 2021 in terms of anime. Jalen, Amber, and I talk about the anime we loved, hated, missed and look ahead to the anime that have caught our eye in 2022. I hope you all had a great holiday season and I can't wait to see what 2022 has in store for all of us. This will be part one of a multipart video series. Stay tuned for part two. 

Hey guys, sorry I've been away for so long, but this monster of a video took a minute to put together. I really tried to finish these videos by Christmas, but you know what they say about the best laid plans... In fact these videos took so long that I needed some help to get it done and it turned out better than I thought. Thank you to Jalen and Amber for their help, I could't have done this without them.
